CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet - Next Year's Hostesses - The Roanoke (Va.) chapter will entertain the GF's in magnificent Gerenbrier [sic] Hotel in White Sulphur Springs, W. Va. Seated : Natalie Clayton, Helene Downing, Polly Weeden and Natalie Holmes.  Standing: Evelyn Skipper, Anne Coleman, La Verne Full...Gladys Fulton, Adelaide Johnson, Julia Law, Anne Patterson, Alyce Moore and Doris Elam"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of members of Roanoke chapter of Girl Friends, Inc., seated: Natalie Clayton, Helene Downing, Polly Weeden, Natalie Holmes; standing: Evelyn Skipper, Anne Coleman, La Verne Full, Gladys Fulton, Adelaide Johnson, Julia Law, Anne Patterson, Alyce Moore, and Doris Elam, posed in Webster Hall
